The evidence with the title 'Truckers are facing a new kind of scrutiny — electronic data tracking ... ' says Sep 17, 2016  ... The new rule is aimed at streamlining enforcement of “ hours of service ” regulations in place for years , a system of Rubik's Cube-like complexity that parses out how much time drivers can drive before needing breaks, how long their breaks need to be, and when they need to be taken, among other things. 
